title: Ash Holme: What Not To Do With Dad
overview: What Not To Do With Dad sees TikTok star and party-animal, Ash Holme take on the types of challenges you would never, EVER want your parent to know about. Only she's taking her dad, Phil, along for the ride.... How will they fare learning to pole dance? Visiting a sex club? Or double dating? And what will they discover about each other - and their relationship - in the process?
